snippet: The airstrike that killed a Palestinian, who was believed to be a militant, and injured two others came hours after a rocket fired from Gaza hit southern Israel.
abstract: Israeli airstrike kills Palestinian who was believed to be a militant as he rode a motorcycle in the northern Gaza Strip; seriously wounds a man accompanying him and a boy who passing by; strike comes hours after a rocket fired from Gaza hit southern Israel.

byline.original: By ISABEL KERSHNER and FARES AKRAM
byline.contributor: Isabel Kershner reported from Jerusalem, and Fares Akram from Gaza.

lead_paragraph: The airstrike that killed a Palestinian, who was believed to be a militant, and injured two others came hours after a rocket fired from Gaza hit southern Israel.

headline.main: Israeli Airstrike in Gaza Strip Kills Palestinian
headline.print_headline: Israeli Airstrike in Gaza Strip Kills Palestinian
